visualizationConfigs.vQuery: MATCH (n:KPI:RESULTS) where n.reportId = 601 and n.kpiId=252 with DISTINCT MAX(n.executionId) as latestExecutionId,n.completionDateEpochTime as completionDateEpochTime MATCH (n:KPI:RESULTS) where n.executionId=latestExecutionId RETURN  completionDateEpochTime , n.Productivity as Productivity ORDER BY completionDateEpochTime DESC
